metadata.description:
Chronicles of the Colorless Rogue: Chapter One is the first of many in the series starring The Colorless Rogue from the Loser Club: The Rogue Collection.

Loser Club is a Web3 Brand with a collection of 10,000 Non Fungible Tokens. The Token consists of art from J'von. Loser Club has an amazing community of which I am apart of.

This is a story of my own creation. A hypothetical post apocalyptic Web3 journey. The Rogue Loser: The Colorless sets off across the Barren OpenSea to find a Magic Paintbrush that belongs to the Rogue King.
metadata.name: Chronicles of the Colorless Rogue: Chapter One
